flowchart TD
    A1[World right-click event] --> B[Normalize trigger context]
    A2[Hotkey binding event] --> B
    A3[Spellcast recovery trigger] --> B

    B --> C[SharedTriggerPipeline source, mode, skipHooked]
    C --> D{Combat lockdown?}
    D -- Yes --> Z1[Abort safely]
    D -- No --> E{Target selected / invalid context?}

    E -- Yes --> Z2[Exit fishing session and clear secure state]
    E -- No --> F{Hooked interact mode active?}

    F -- Yes --> G{Hook evidence present?}
    G -- No --> H[Clear stale hooked state]
    G -- Yes --> I[Configure interact loot secure action]
    I --> S[Await hardware click]
    H --> J[Continue pre-cast path]

    F -- No --> J[Continue pre-cast path]

    J --> K{Transient buff block?}
    K -- Yes --> Z3[Warn and stop]
    K -- No --> L[Ensure secure frames]

    L --> M[ConfigureFishingClickAction]
    M --> N[Build macro/action in strict order]
    N --> O{Cast armed now?}
    O -- No --> P[Pre-cast consumable step only]
    O -- Yes --> Q[Pre-cast state and timers]

    P --> S
    Q --> S
    S --> T[Secure button click executes action]
    T --> U[State machine receives cast/loot events]